    %% Connections
    Toolbar -->|updates| UIStore
    UIStore -->|triggers resize| GridView
    GridView -->|renders| PreviewRenderer
    PreviewRenderer -->|invoke via| PreviewService

    PreviewService -->|calls| GenPreview
    PreviewService -->|calls| GenPyramid
    PreviewService -->|calls| GenBatch

    GenPreview -->|routes to| GenThumb
    GenPyramid -->|calls all 3| GenThumb
    GenPyramid -->|calls all 3| GenStdPreview
    GenPyramid -->|calls all 3| GenNative

    GenThumb -->|uses config| Sizes
    GenStdPreview -->|uses config| Sizes
    GenNative -->|uses config| Sizes

    GenThumb -->|respects| Quality
    GenThumb -->|enforces| MaxSize
    GenThumb -->|writes to| CacheDir

    PreviewEnum -.->|defines types| PreviewSvc
    CalcDim -->|computes| Sizes

    CacheDir --> ImageFiles
    ImageFiles -->|loaded by| PreviewService

